---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '@layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Story"
  description="Meet the guide behind JaJa Tours. Learn how a passion for South Africa's wild places became a life of leading adventures."
>
  <section class="story-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
      <h1>Built on dust roads and open water.</h1>
      <p class="story-lead">
        JaJa Tours started the way most good things do — with one person who
        couldn't stop exploring and a circle of friends who wanted in.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-body">
    <div class="container story-grid">
      <div class="story-content">
        <h2>From weekend trips to a way of life</h2>
        <p>
          What began as informal overland weekends through the Cederberg and
          Garden Route evolved into something bigger. Friends brought friends.
          Routes got longer. The logistics got sharper. And the idea of sharing
          South Africa's wildest corners with curious travelers became a
          full-time pursuit.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today JaJa runs handcrafted expeditions across nine provinces — from
          dive windows on the Aliwal Shoal to canyon descents in Mpumalanga,
          bushveld camps in Limpopo, and surf points along the Wild Coast.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-values">
        <article>
          <h3>Local Knowledge</h3>
          <p>
            Every route is scouted in person. We know the roads, the tides,
            and the seasons because we live them year-round.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Small by Design</h3>
          <p>
            Groups max at ten. This means faster transitions, deeper
            conversations, and the freedom to take detours when something
            unexpected appears.
          </p>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Safety First</h3>
          <p>
            Certified guides, maintained equipment, and contingency plans for
            every environment — river, reef, or ridgeline.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="story-cta">
    <div class="container cta-shell">
      <h2>Want to see where we go next?</h2>
      <p>Browse upcoming routes or tell us what kind of adventure you are chasing.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/tours" class="button-primary">Browse Tours</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="button-secondary">Get in Touch</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .story-hero {
    padding: 0.7rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .story-hero h1 {
    margin: 0.95rem 0 1.05rem;
    max-width: 16ch;
  }

  .story-lead {
    max-width: 52ch;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .story-body {
    padding: 1rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .story-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.6rem;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 18ch;
  }

  .story-content p + p {
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
  }

  .story-values {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.8rem;
  }

  .story-values article {
    padding: 1.1rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-card-border);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.74);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(18, 36, 51, 0.08);
  }

  .story-values h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  .story-values p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-cta {
    padding: 0.6rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .cta-shell {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 1.6rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border: 1px solid rgba(18, 36, 51, 0.15);
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 85% 10%, rgba(240, 183, 99, 0.45), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(158deg, rgba(255, 253, 248, 0.96), rgba(239, 249, 250, 0.86));
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .cta-shell h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .cta-shell p {
    margin: 0 auto 1.1rem;
    max-width: 46ch;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  @media (min-width: 980px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      align-items: start;
    }

    .story-values {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-shell {
      padding: 2.1rem 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>
